graph TB
    subgraph "User Interaction Layer"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
        Notebooks[Notebooks<br/>JupyterLab/RStudio/VS Code]
    end

    subgraph "Core ML Platform Components"
        KServe[KServe<br/>Model Serving]
        DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Kubeflow Pipelines v2]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Metadata & Versioning]
        MLflow[MLflow<br/>Experiment Tracking]
        Feast[Feast<br/>Feature Store]
    end

    subgraph "Training Infrastructure"
        Trainer[Kubeflow Trainer<br/>Distributed Training & LLM Fine-tuning]
        TrainingOperator[Training Operator<br/>PyTorch/TensorFlow/XGBoost/MPI/JAX]
        KubeRay[KubeRay<br/>Ray Cluster Management]
    end

    subgraph "LLM & AI Services"
        LlamaStack[Llama Stack Operator<br/>LLM Inference]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>Explainability & Guardrails]
    end

    subgraph "Controllers & Extensions"
        NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller<br/>Gateway API Integration]
        ModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>Routes & NetworkPolicies]
    end

    subgraph "Infrastructure Dependencies"
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>Traffic Management & mTLS]
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>Serverless Autoscaling]
        Argo[Argo Workflows<br/>Pipeline Execution]
        GatewayAPI[Gateway API<br/>Ingress Routing]
        S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Model/Data Artifacts]
        PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL<br/>Metadata Storage]
    end

    %% User interactions
    Dashboard -->|manages| Notebooks
    Dashboard -->|manages| KServe
    Dashboard -->|manages| DSP
    Dashboard -->|manages| ModelRegistry
    Dashboard -->|manages| MLflow
    Dashboard -->|manages| Feast

    %% Notebooks integrations
    Notebooks -->|submits pipelines| DSP
    Notebooks -->|calls inference| KServe
    Notebooks -->|logs experiments| MLflow
    Notebooks -->|retrieves features| Feast
    Notebooks -->|registers models| ModelRegistry

    %% KServe dependencies
    KServe -->|uses| Istio
    KServe -->|uses| Knative
    KServe -->|extended by| ModelController
    KServe -->|loads models from| S3
    KServe -->|reads metadata from| ModelRegistry

    %% Pipeline dependencies
    DSP -->|orchestrates via| Argo
    DSP -->|stores artifacts in| S3
    DSP -->|stores metadata in| PostgreSQL
    DSP -->|deploys models to| KServe
    DSP -->|registers to| ModelRegistry

    %% Training dependencies
    Trainer -->|downloads data from| S3
    Trainer -->|logs to| MLflow
    Trainer -->|saves models to| S3
    Trainer -->|registers to| ModelRegistry
    TrainingOperator -->|supports| Trainer

    %% Feast dependencies
    Feast -->|stores features in| PostgreSQL
    Feast -->|serves to| KServe
    Feast -->|serves to| Notebooks

    %% MLflow dependencies
    MLflow -->|stores in| PostgreSQL
    MLflow -->|stores artifacts in| S3
    MLflow -->|uses| GatewayAPI

    %% Model Registry dependencies
    ModelRegistry -->|stores in| PostgreSQL
    ModelRegistry -->|used by| KServe
    ModelRegistry -->|used by| DSP
    ModelRegistry -->|used by| Notebooks

    %% Notebook Controller
    NotebookController -->|creates| GatewayAPI
    NotebookController -->|manages| Notebooks

    %% TrustyAI
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|stores metrics in| PostgreSQL

    %% LLM Services
    LlamaStack -->|alternative to| KServe
    ModelController -->|extends| KServe

